      "writtenOn": "2020-11-19T15:33:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "There are no real security concerns here, we fuzz skps.\n\nIf you wanted to be extra paranoid you could reject any URLs whose domain didn\u0027t match *.skia.org.\n\nIf we want to also allow loading skps from certain Google Cloud Storage buckets\nyou would also want to have an approved bucket list that filtered for URLs\nthat looked like:\n\n  https://storage.googleapis.com/bucket-name/*",
