      "writtenOn": "2020-11-19T16:16:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "My main concern was adding a potential vector for social engineering - e.g. \"go check out this innocent looking debugger page\" which actually loads data using the person\u0027s cookies, maybe fetching data that should normally be protected.\n\nIt seems unlikely to matter much, but I wanted to bring it up.",
